prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a party hat, hilariously attempting to blow out a single, very determined candle on a tiny cupcake that it's holding. The sloth has a look of comical exertion, with puffed-out cheeks. The background is a soft wash of celebratory confetti-like splotches in pastel teals, yellows, and pinks. Centered below the sloth, in beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday... eventually". The entire image is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges.
